<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3037467357" lastPageId="30" lastPageNumber="30" pageId="29" pageNumber="29">7 females (AMNH *266010, *266011, *267837, *267839; MNHN *1995.820, 1995.821, *1995.822), and 4 males (AMNH *267088, *267280, *267838, MNHN *1995.819); see table 4 for measurements.</materialsCitation>
